snippet.title: Windjammers 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready! The legendary disc throwing game, Windjammers, is getting a sequel!
Windjammers 2 will combine everything fans love about the classic title with entirely hand-drawn 2D animations to create the ultimate windjamming experience. 

Windjammers 2 will fly onto Nintendo Switch and PC. For complete information on Windjammers, hit up www.flyingpowerdisc.com
